Cohesity reports local users, local groups, and AD groups added to the cluster.
Cohesity does not show the individual AD users inside those AD groups. That membership would require querying Active Directory through the integration team.
Dell Technologies Data Domain currently generates only user information through the available API. Group details are not available through the current endpoint.
A case is open with Dell Technologies to validate whether group details can be retrieved through an alternate API or through LDAP configuration data exposing AD group mappings.
